OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FMorocco-born killer Ahmed Alid came to
OL,7,Fthe UK to seek asylum having drifted
OL,8,Faround Europe for years.
OL,10,FThe former pastry chef and shop owner,
OL,11,Fconvicted of randomly murdering a
OL,12,Fpensioner walking in Hartlepool town
OL,13,Fcentre, told jurors during his trial
OL,14,Fhe had been jailed in Germany for
OL,15,Fentering the country without a
OL,16,Fpassport or visa.
OL,18,FThe 45-year-old was born in Fez,
OL,19,FMorocco, but was raised in Algeria,
OL,20,Fwhere his grandfather had a business.
