OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FHe left North Africa in 2007, telling
OL,7,FTeesside Crown Court via an Arabic
OL,8,Finterpreter how his shop had been
OL,9,Fmonitored by the intelligence services
OL,10,Fwho were "harassing" him.
OL,12,FHe arrived in Spain and moved around
OL,13,Fthe continent for years, spending time
OL,14,Fin Spain, France, Italy, Germany,
OL,15,FScandinavia, the Netherlands and
OL,16,FAustria, never gaining asylum.
OL,18,FAlid spent just days or weeks in some
OL,19,Fcountries and years in Germany, where
OL,20,Fhe never achieved his aim of opening a
OL,21,Fshop.
