OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FHe tried to marry a German woman but
OL,7,Fhad lost his passport in Greece, he
OL,8,Ftold the court, so the marriage could
OL,9,Fnot go through.
OL,11,FLate in 2020, he took a ferry from
OL,12,FAmsterdam to Middlesbrough where he
OL,13,Fwas arrested by police as he did not
OL,14,Fhave the correct papers and he applied
OL,15,Ffor asylum.
OL,17,FAsked by John Elvidge KC, his defence
OL,18,Fcounsel, if that was successful, Alid
OL,19,Fsaid: "I didn't have any answer."
