OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FHis asylum status was still being
OL,7,Fprocessed at the time of the murder of
OL,8,FTerence Carney in the street in
OL,9,FHartlepool on 15 October last year, it
OL,10,Fwas understood.
OL,12,FHe was permitted to work four hours a
OL,13,Fweek, but that did not lead to him
OL,14,Fgetting a job, and he was often seen
OL,15,Fjogging around Hartlepool to keep fit.
OL,17,FAlid was a devout Muslim and prayed
OL,18,Ffive times a day at home, but did not
OL,19,Fattend a local mosque.
