OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FHe clashed with other asylum seekers
OL,7,Fliving at the Home Office-approved
OL,8,Faccommodation in Wharton Terrace, in
OL,9,FHartlepool, including arguments about
OL,10,Fhis cleanliness and them leaving
OL,11,Falcohol in the communal fridge, which
OL,12,Fhe said was against his religious
OL,13,Fbeliefs.
OL,15,FIn the days leading up to the attack,
OL,16,Fthey grew concerned about his reaction
OL,17,Fto the Hamas attacks on Israel.
