OL,3,CMurderer 'came to UK to seek asylum
OL,4,Cafter drifting around Europe for years'
OL,6,FJaved Nouri, the man he tried to
OL,7,Fmurder as he slept in his bed, told
OL,8,Fpolice later: "He was sitting on the
OL,9,Fkitchen chair and checking the news on
OL,10,Fhis mobile phone.
OL,12,F"He was laughing and every time they
OL,13,Fwould kill somebody, he would praise
OL,14,FGod."
OL,16,FHe added: "I was very upset from that
OL,17,Fnight and I have seen something
OL,18,Fterrible and frightening in his eyes."
